org.senchalabs.gwt.gwtdriver.by

Class CheatingByChained

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openqa.selenium.By
      • org.senchalabs.gwt.gwtdriver.by.CheatingByChained

  • public class CheatingByChained
extends org.openqa.selenium.By
    When looking for only one item, cheats by only looking for one item at each level. Useful only if you want the first result of each By operation, otherwise use FasterByChained or ByChained.

    When running SearchContext.findElements(org.openqa.selenium.By) to search for multiple items, uses ByChained normal.
